____

____all currently enrolled in the guild Hand of Judgement . . .
____Baroness Melwen Shadowbow a High Elf Cleric of Tunare of 61 Seasons &
____Brangvyne Nimloth a Wood Elf Ranger of Tunare of 52 Seasons live.
____My other toons include . . .
____Xenawyr - 55 Druidess
____Moriel - 35 Shadow Knight
____Linnathon - 33 Enchantress
____
____Thought I would pop in and see how everyone was doing or if anyone

____
____If anyone plays on Xegony I would love to meet you and say hi, or if
____you fall in groupable range of any of those toons to adventure a bit
____together.
____
____/Hugs to All
____Bran
